import React from "react";
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

function InkaWall() {
  return (

    <Link to="/inkawall1">

  <svg className="painting inkawall"

      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsosb="http://www.openswatchbook.org/uri/2009/osb"
      width="4036.8"
      height="2904"
      version="1.1"
      viewBox="0 0 4036.8 2904"
    >
      <defs>
        <linearGradient osbpaint="solid">
          <stop offset="0" stopColor="#000" stopOpacity="1"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient osbpaint="solid">
          <stop offset="0" stopColor="#d3d3d3" stopOpacity="1"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
        <marker orient="auto" overflow="visible" refX="0" refY="0">
          <path
            fill="#000"
            fillOpacity="1"
            fillRule="evenodd"
            stroke="#000"
            strokeOpacity="1"
            strokeWidth=".8pt"
            d="M10 0l4-4L0 0l14 4z"
          ></path>
        </marker>
      </defs>
      <g
        strokeDasharray="none"
        strokeLinecap="square"
        strokeMiterlimit="4"
        strokeOpacity="1"
        strokeWidth="15"
        display="inline"
        paintOrder="fill markers stroke"
        transform="translate(-1130.4 -420)"
      >
        <g fill="none" fillOpacity="1" stroke="#000">
          <path
            d="M1507.2 2928v-192h547.2v-576h-547.2v-960h547.2V624h-729.6v192H1872v192h-547.2v1344H1872v192h-547.2v576"
            opacity="0.993"
          ></path>
          <path
            d="M1324.8 3120h1094.4V1776H1872v-192h547.2V816h729.6v192h-547.2v1344h547.2v192h-547.2v576H3696V1776h-547.2v-192H3696V816h729.6v192h-547.2v1344h547.2v192h-547.2v576h1094.4V1776h-547.2v-192h547.2V624h-182.4v768h-547.2v576h547.2v960h-729.6v-192H4608v-576h-547.2v-960H4608V624H3513.6v768h-547.2v576h547.2v960H2784v-192h547.2v-576H2784v-960h547.2V624H2236.8v768h-547.2v576h547.2v960h-729.6"
            opacity="0.993"
          ></path>
        </g>
        <path
          fill="#000"
          fillOpacity="0"
          stroke="#d3d3d3"
          d="M1142.4 432H5155.200000000001V3312H1142.4z"
          opacity="0.993"
        ></path>
      </g>
    </svg>

</Link>

  );



}

export default InkaWall;
